1975;;Inn of the Damned;;Australian;;Terry Bourke;;Judith Anderson, Michael Craig, Alex Cord, John Meillon;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inn_of_the_Damned;;In 1896, a crazed woman and her husband run an inn in eastern Victoria and take revenge for the deaths of their children years before. A bounty hunter arrives to investigate the mysterious deaths of many people and puts an end to the killing.